&lt;p data-start=&quot;308&quot; data-end=&quot;528&quot;&gt;As a Forward Deployment Engineer, you’ll help drive the growth of Speechmatics by working directly with customers, partners, and developer communities to demonstrate, integrate, customise, and deploy our Voice AI, fast.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;530&quot; data-end=&quot;939&quot;&gt;You’ll operate at the intersection of engineering, product, and adoption. Part product evangelist, part hands-on builder, you’ll implement our Voice AI in demos, Proofs of Concept, pilots, and full-scale production environments. You’ll also engage with the wider developer ecosystem, building examples, running workshops, supporting integrations, and helping developers unlock the full potential of our APIs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;941&quot; data-end=&quot;1165&quot;&gt;This is a deeply hands-on role. You’ll work side-by-side with end-users, customer engineering teams, developer communities, and our internal engineering organisation t

&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Marketing Director to lead the growth of Squarespace Domains. For over two decades, Squarespace has defined the future of web design and helped entrepreneurs make their ideas and passions an online reality. At the same time, Squarespace has grown into one of the world&#39;s biggest domain providers, with millions of customers entrusting Squarespace with a vital part of their online brand identity - their domain.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role offers the chance to lead marketing for a product that&#39;s essential for every small business, entrepreneur, or individual with a creative idea. You will report to the Senior Director, Marketing - Domains &amp;amp; Applications, and work remote from a US approved state or hybrid from our NYC Headquarters.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll Get To… &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
