&lt;p&gt;The Toast POS app is the central pillar of Toast’s restaurant products. Every day, hundreds of thousands of servers, hosts, bartenders, and chefs use Toast’s POS to serve millions of guests. Our POS product is constantly evolving, and the POS Productivity team builds the platform that makes this evolution possible.&lt;/p&gt;
